@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    .privacy-section {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 60px 0;
    }

    .privacy-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

        .privacy-header h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

    .privacy-content {
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

        .privacy-content h3 {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .privacy-content p, .privacy-content ul {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .privacy-content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
</style>

<!-- Privacy Policy Section -->
<div class="container privacy-section">
    <div class="privacy-header">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="privacy-content">
        <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
        <p>Welcome to [Your Institution/Lab Name]’s Equipment Management and Lab Experiment Platform. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform for slot booking and lab experiments.</p>

        <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, student/staff ID.</li>
            <li><strong>Booking Information:</strong> Slot details, equipment requested, experiment details.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Log data, IP address, browser type, access times.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Manage slot bookings and lab experiment schedules.</li>
            <li>Ensure proper usage and maintenance of lab equipment.</li>
            <li>Improve system functionality and user experience.</li>
            <li>Comply with institutional and legal requirements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4. Data Sharing and Security</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>We do not sell or rent your data to third parties.</li>
            <li>Your data is only accessible to authorized personnel for operational purposes.</li>
            <li>We implement security measures to protect against unauthorized access or misuse.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
        <p>We may use cookies to enhance user experience and track usage patterns. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

        <h3>6. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>We retain your data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes stated in this policy unless a longer retention period is required by law.</p>

        <h3>7. Your Rights and Choices</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
            <li>Opt out of non-essential communications.</li>
            <li>Request information about how your data is processed.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>8. Third-Party Links</h3>
        <p>Our platform may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy policies or content.</p>

        <h3>9. Changes to This Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Significant changes will be notified via email or platform announcements.</p>

        <h3>10. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>For questions or concerns about this policy, contact us.</p>
    </div>
</div>
